[div class=p 
	[em 
		"BurgerTime
	]em
	" is a port of the classic 1982 arcade game, released by Mattel Electronics in 1983 after they acquired the rights to the title from Data East. The player controls Peter Pepper, who must walk over giant hamburger toppings to send them to lower floors, eventually forming complete burgers. Players must avoid the enemies Hot Dog, Mr. Pickle, and Mr. Egg while building burgers, or crush them under falling ingredients.
	$LF
]div
